cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "OpenEtruscan — open-source digital corpus platform for Etruscan epigraphy"
message: "If you use this software or the OpenEtruscan corpus, please cite both this software entry and the dataset deposit (see preferred-citation)."
type: software
authors:
